title: Italy expected to look right as polls open in national election
description: Polls opened Sunday in the Italian national elections, with the far-right Brothers of Italy party -- led by Giorgia Meloni -- poised to make big gains after the collapse of two governments since the last election.

title: North Korea fires ballistic missile into waters off east coast of Korean peninsula
description: North Korea has fired a ballistic missile into the waters off the east coast of the Korean peninsula, according to officials in both South Korea and Japan.
